25
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:43,329
<i>and in terms of</i>
<i>transforming people's lives.</i>

26
00:02:43,897 --> 00:02:46,195
<i>We are coming to Chicago,</i>

27
00:02:46,299 --> 00:02:49,291
<i>at the time of</i>
