David Dellinger,

87
00:06:05,598 --> 00:06:07,088
Rennie Davis, and Thomas Hayden...

88
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:13,332
Who is the one that shook his fist
in the direction of the jury?

89
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:15,304
