672
00:42:52,469 --> 00:42:54,369
<i>Please obey the law.</i>

673
00:42:55,506 --> 00:42:57,371
Get the fucking pigs!

674
00:42:59,343 --> 00:43:00,935
Get the car!

675
00:43:06,884 --> 00:43:08,715
- Hell, no, we won't go!
- Hell, no, we won't go!

676
00:43:08,819 --> 00:43:10,912
- Hell, no, we won't go!
- Hell, no, we won't go!

677
00:43:11,021 --> 00:43:12,579
- Hell, no, we won't go!
