678
00:43:41,018 --> 00:43:44,249
Is anybody hurt? Is anybody hurt?

679
00:43:49,293 --> 00:43:50,317
Mike?

680
00:43:51,729 --> 00:43:53,924
<i>Now, from your own observations</i>

681
00:43:54,031 --> 00:43:57,489
<i>at the Democratic National Convention</i>
<i>on these nights,</i>

682
00:43:57,635 --> 00:44:01,230
<i>did you see any policemen</i>
